 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   Plot Outline :                                                   ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ                                                                    ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   First-time actor Michel Tarrazon plays the young Franois,       ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   a provincial orphan whose destructive behaviour precipitates     ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   his relocation from the home of a long-term foster family        ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   to the care of a benevolent elderly couple. In the course        ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   of this transition, Pialats film presents the turbulence         ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   of Francois' unmoored existence, and his explosive               ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
 ﾞﾛﾛ ｰ   reactions to the contradictory emotions it engenders.            ｰ ﾛﾛﾝ
